@209  = ~Perhaps I wanted it that way. Why are you always interfering in my business?!~
@210  = ~Then I shall stand by your side to make sure that such a thing will not happen again. Is it your dark side revealing itself here? (sigh) It is a cruel fate you have to cope with, <CHARNAME>. Do not embrace it.~
